title: Hand Up, We Were Dead Wrong...
description:
Domonique and Charlie start off with a recap of MNF and workshop some hot takes before diving into the biggest moments from Week 3. Then, Dom explains why we were dead wrong before Ashley Foxworth returns to give more Roses and Thorns.
